## OWebDataStore.get() method

Gets data with the given key.

When the key is a regexp all data with a key name that match the given regexp will be returned in an object.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
get(key: string | RegExp): any;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  key | string \| RegExp | The data key name. |

<b>Returns:</b>

any
